quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  46,6,"And when mankind is herded, those(false gods) become enemies to them and deny their worship of them."
  46,7,"And when Our signsc are read to them, evident, those who deny say of the truth when it has come to them, “This is evident sorcery.”"
  46,8,"Or do they say, “He has fabricated it!” Saysg , “If I have fabricated it myself, there is nothing youpl can do to protect me from Allah. He knows better what you are engaged in; sufficient is He as a witness between me and you, and He is the Oft-Forgiving, the Bestower of mercy.”"
  46,9,"Saysg , “I am not different from the other messengers, and I do not know what will be done with me or with youpl . I only follow what is revealed to me, and I am only an evident warner.”"
  46,10,"Saysg , “Have youpl seen: if it is truly from Allah and you deny it? And a witness from the Children of Israel has testified to its like and has attained faith, while you have acted arrogantly. Indeed, Allah does not guide the unjust people.”"